German Troops Targeted in Afghanistan Attack, One Dead

-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 
2011-06-02T11:05:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-02/german-troops-targeted-in-afghanistan-attack-six-may-be-injured.html
German troops were the target of an
attack that killed one soldier and injured five others in
 Afghanistan  today, the Bundeswehr army said.  The attack took place about 36 kilometers south of Kunduz,
where the soldiers’ tank was hit by an explosion, according to
the Bundeswehr army’s website. The injured soldiers are being
treated in the emergency center of the reconstruction team in
Kunduz, according to the website.  Relatives of the victims have been informed, the website
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Julie Cruz in Frankfurt at 
 jcruz6@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
